snippet: The medical examiner’s office worked on Tuesday to determine the cause of death for Ms. Scott, the fashion designer who was found dead in her apartment on Monday.
abstract: New York City medical examiner’s office is working to determine the cause of death for fashion designer L’Wren Scott, who was found dead in her Manhattan apartment; police say her death was most likely suicide but medical examiner's office has not finalized its determination.

byline.original: By EMMA G. FITZSIMMONS and JOSEPH GOLDSTEIN

lead_paragraph: The medical examiner’s office worked on Tuesday to determine the cause of death for Ms. Scott, the fashion designer who was found dead in her apartment on Monday.

headline.main: L’Wren Scott’s Death Still Under Investigation
